# Garbage Collection

## What gets collected

This report surfaces candidates for cleanup:

- Stale docs (not reviewed in >90 days)
- Oversized files (>500KB with no good reason)
- Suspicious filenames (`final-final`, `v2`, `copy of`, etc.)
- `TODO` / `FIXME` clusters that never got addressed
- Docs not linked from `docs/agent/index.md`

